        "description": "Test case: Filter theo loại vận chuyển\n\nExpected Result:\n- Chỉ trả về routes có route_type = SEA\n- Loại bỏ AIR, LAND, MULTIMODAL routes"
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "7. Combined Constraints (Vaccine Shipment)",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1/analytics/route-optimization?origin=VNSGN&destination=USNYC&maxAlarmRate=0.05&maxTransitStops=2&maxRoutes=3",
          "protocol": "http",
          "host": ["localhost"],
          "port": "3000",
          "path": ["api", "v1", "analytics", "route-optimization"],
          "query": [
            {
              "key": "origin",
              "value": "VNSGN"
            },
            {
              "key": "destination",
              "value": "USNYC"
            },
            {
              "key": "maxAlarmRate",
              "value": "0.05",
              "description": "Strict safety requirement"
            },
            {
              "key": "maxTransitStops",
              "value": "2",
              "description": "Minimize handling"
            },
            {
              "key": "maxRoutes",
              "value": "3",
              "description": "Top 3 only"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Test case: Realistic scenario cho vaccine shipment\n\nConstraints:\n- maxAlarmRate = 5% (high safety)\n- maxTransitStops = 2 (minimize handling)\n- maxRoutes = 3 (focused options)\n\nExpected Result:\n- Routes phù hợp cho hàng nhạy cảm\n- Có insights về safety và recommendations"
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "8. Error: Missing Origin",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1/analytics/route-optimization?destination=USNYC",
          "protocol": "http",
          "host": ["localhost"],
          "port": "3000",
          "path": ["api", "v1", "analytics", "route-optimization"],
          "query": [
            {
              "key": "destination",
              "value": "USNYC"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Test case: Validation error - missing origin\n\nExpected Result:\n- Status: 400 Bad Request\n- Error: MISSING_PARAMETERS\n- Message: Both origin and destination ports are required"
      },
      "response": []
    },
